''Magus Borealis'', the Red Mage of the North, leads the fascist ["Elf"]s, ["ReignDeer"], and ["PolerBear"]s from the upper bergs in a ceaseless war against the anarchist ["Penguin"] horde of the nether ["Austra"]l face of the world. Magus hates children and is seldom seen without his ["Booz"].

